            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block"> <h1 class="hero-title">Transform Your Body, Transform Your Life</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">Join our fitness community and achieve your goals with personalized training programs and expert guidance.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1954524/pexels-photo-1954524.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2" class="d-block">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2017/04/22/10/15/woman-2250970_1280.jpg" class="d-block">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1614928228253-dc09cbc3b11c?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" class="d-block">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2017/04/25/20/18/woman-2260736_1280.jpg" class="d-block">
